OL,3,CAnimal-loving grandad named as alleged
OL,4,Cvictim in suspected hit and run
OL,6,FTributes have been paid to a grandad
OL,7,Fwho died in an alleged hit and run in
OL,8,FIngleby Barwick.
OL,10,FBrian Darby, 60, died in the alleged
OL,11,Fincident in the Myton Way area of the
OL,12,Ftown on the evening of Friday 9
OL,13,FFebruary.
OL,15,FTwo men, aged 29 and 56, have been
OL,16,Fcharged in connection with the
OL,17,Fincident and will appear at Teesside
OL,18,FCrown Court on Wednesday 14 February.
