OL,6,FMr Darby's identity was confirmed by
OL,7,FCleveland Police on Tuesday (13
OL,8,FFebruary) and his family have honoured
OL,9,Fhis memory in a statement.
OL,11,FIt read: "We are completely
OL,12,Fheartbroken at the sudden loss of our
OL,13,Fbeautiful Brian. Nobody could ever
OL,14,Funderstand just how much he meant to
OL,15,Fus all.
OL,17,F"He was special in so many ways. He
OL,18,Fwas an absolute gentleman who cared so
OL,19,Fmuch about people. He always made time
OL,20,Ffor us, nothing was ever too much
OL,21,Ftrouble for him.
