OL,3,CAnimal-loving grandad named as alleged
OL,4,Cvictim in suspected hit and run
OL,6,F"Brian lived life to the full, he
OL,7,Fnever wasted a moment. He loved to
OL,8,Fsocialise and everyone adored being
OL,9,Faround him. Brian was also a proud
OL,10,Fgrandad and his future with his
OL,11,Fgrandchildren has now been taken away
OL,12,Ffrom him.
OL,14,F"We are grateful for the kind words of
OL,15,Fsupport from the community but we
OL,16,Frespectfully ask that we are now given
OL,17,Fsome privacy to allow us to process
OL,18,Fwhat has happened as a family."
