OL,3,CAnimal-loving grandad named as alleged
OL,4,Cvictim in suspected hit and run
OL,6,FMr Darby worked at Saltholme Nature
OL,7,FReserve where he was a "hugely
OL,8,Fpopular" member of the team.
OL,10,F"We are saddened to share the news
OL,11,Fthat our dear colleague Brian Darby
OL,12,Fpassed away on Friday evening," a
OL,13,Fstatement on the reserve's Facebook
OL,14,Fpage read. "Our thoughts are with his
OL,15,Ffriends and family at this really
OL,16,Fdifficult time, as well as the wider
OL,17,Fcommunity.
