OL,3,CAnimal-loving grandad named as alleged
OL,4,Cvictim in suspected hit and run
OL,6,F"Brian was a hugely popular member of
OL,7,Fthe team at RSPB Saltholme. He joined
OL,8,Fus in 2022 as a senior project manager
OL,9,Fand quickly fell in love with nature,
OL,10,Fgetting involved with whatever life on
OL,11,Fa nature reserve threw at him, whether
OL,12,Fthat was getting stuck in wet
OL,13,Fgrassland or washing up stints in the
OL,14,Fcafe.
OL,16,F"His enthusiasm was infectious,
OL,17,Fespecially when out and about with
OL,18,Fcolleagues spotting wildlife. He will
OL,19,Fbe greatly missed by everyone who knew
OL,20,Fhim and worked with him."
